import React from 'react'
import { AboutCont, About, AboutTitle, PICont, MeCont, SkillsCont,
MeTitle } from '../Components/AboutMe/AboutMe.elements'

function AboutPage() {
  return (
    <About  id='AboutMe'>
      <AboutCont>
        <AboutTitle>About Me</AboutTitle>
        <PICont>
          <MeCont>

          </MeCont>
          <SkillsCont>
            Skills
          </SkillsCont>
        </PICont>
      </AboutCont>
    </About>
  )
}

export default AboutPage
